1) edt [optional name]
2) save from within nvim
^repeat those steps as needed


echo $WEB_FNAME for sanity
pan [optional name]
pub

to edit (once published):
edt [name] 
pan [name]

to unpublish:
nvim $PROJ_DIR\posts_main.md
(remove the line linking to the post)
jpan posts_main
mv $PROJ_DIR/posts/finished/$1.md $PROJ_DIR/posts/drafts/
rm PROJ_DIR\posts\drafts\$1.hmtl

republish:
unpublish
edt (as many times as necessary)
pan [name]
pub [name]
